subject: JUnit 3.8 and VAJava
msgSnippet: I just installed JUnit 3.8 into VAJava 4.03.  Now when I run with the swing ui and make a change to the code, JUnit evaporates. This is not the behavior I see
messageBody:
I just installed JUnit 3.8 into VAJava 4.03. Now when I run with the swing
ui and make a change to the code, JUnit evaporates.

This is not the behavior I see with 3.7.

Randy Cox
